@startuml
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #EEEBDC
  BorderColor #333333
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor User

rectangle "Frontend\n(Vue.js)" as Frontend
rectangle "Backend\n(Flask)" as Backend
rectangle "Model Serving\n(TensorFlow Serving)" as ModelServing
rectangle "Model Repository" as ModelRepo
cloud "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
database "Redis" as Redis
database "PostgreSQL" as PostgreSQL

User --> Frontend : Uploads image
Frontend --> Backend : API requests
Backend --> ModelServing : Inference requests
Backend --> Cloudinary : Store/retrieve assets
Backend --> Redis : Caching/session management
Backend --> PostgreSQL : Data persistence
ModelServing --> ModelRepo : Load model
Backend --> ModelRepo : Model retraining (potential)

note right of Backend
  API Gateway
  Data collection
  Orchestration
end note

note bottom of ModelRepo
  DeblurGAN-V2 model
  Training scripts
end note

@enduml